rực diện, quyền lực hoàng gia ... xiềng xích bị chặn giữa hai người, và cả hai không ngừng tiến về phía trước, chỉ để ở bên nhau trong giây lát.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"217438","season":1,"vote_average":8,"vote_count":1},"modified":"2025-04-12T12:48:46.000Z","cast":["Chu Lệ Lam","Lý Phi","Zhang Jingyun","Zhao Xilin","Li Wenru","Zhou Weiwei"],"director":["Lý Ngọc Hi"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chu Lệ Lam","name_vi":"Chu Lệ Lam","name_original":"Zhu Lilan","tmdb_id":2232320,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hZGEtqFWCFR5WgGN4AGtquJkLlC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2232320"},{"name":"Lý Phi","name_vi":"Lý Phi","name_original":"Richard Li","tmdb_id":3264069,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cZRBQnxvNTulyL2aBrUMu0RjMoh.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3264069"},{"name":"Zhang Jingyun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhang Jingyun","tmdb_id":3895280,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l96qPaucPWpboSIquSWpJ34GdBw.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3895280"},{"name":"Zhao Xilin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhao Xilin","tmdb_id":4406419,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lAcpGedsD2yzHplkBnUBo5BH190.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4406419"},{"name":"Li Wenru","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Li Wenru","tmdb_id":4234284,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y4nVAZwWdji8EO2IFV8qO5KFwJM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4234284"},{"name":"Zhou Weiwei","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhou Weiwei","tmdb_id":4352487,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rjDFyOFIUXN1aq92GBFmyyUWbMX.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4352487"}],"keywords":[],"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gotvtop102/pjs102@main/pubjs/lo/loi-hua-bat-tu.json"}